{"tid":798382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】洪欣晒恩愛支持老公 張丹峰告誹謗：絕不姑息","createTime":"2018-08-29T09:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T15:58:26.000Z","uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"352b78757c03633aea1d8bb8549e015e7e8e8eb0","tid":798382,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"46歲洪欣與37歲老公張丹峰結婚9年，上月老公傳跟經理人畢瀅似有曖昧（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2v1NPJn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2v1NPJn&d=Y6%2BhmZRuZm2cBO01iDldpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e646f4b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2v1NPJn</a> ），洪欣挺身力撐老公冇出軌，畢瀅亦否認緋聞，張丹峰工作室則表示會追究到底，前晚張丹峰在微博留言：「首批侵權案件已完成持續20天的取證工作，對於誹謗侵權行為，張丹峰工作室都將追究到底，絕不姑息。」<br />\n<br />\n張丹峰轉貼工作室聲明，指為維護合法權益不受侵害，已委托律師團隊，就近期誹謗、侮辱等侵害其名譽權之行為進行起訴維權。洪欣亦有點讚老公呢條帖文，另外上載同老公黐撐枱腳相，兩公婆黐頭芒晒恩愛，洪欣留言：「今晚潮州菜！yummy yummy！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/171847_b45a64907e87f73b9048f4e2cd1e4a52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F171847_b45a64907e87f73b9048f4e2cd1e4a52.png&h=44eb64f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61ac26146a5e4931d6a1c659c6c1ec7dd48da55b","tid":798382,"uid":17545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 潮州菜<br />\n<br />\n劉鑾雄（英語：Joseph Lau Luen-hung，1951年7月21日－[4][1]），別稱「大劉」，籍貫廣東潮州，香港企業家，華人置業公司前任董事會主席和行政總裁[5]。"},{"pid":"e3f0ef81ceb07acc447a215093fb07c777292b05","tid":798382,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" c